WEBVTT

00:03.520 --> 00:04.080
Yu'er

00:04.600 --> 00:06.040
Come let the empress see you

00:23.480 --> 00:24.640
How can this be?

00:25.320 --> 00:26.080
Right

00:26.200 --> 00:27.600
How can he not follow orders?

00:27.640 --> 00:28.720
Rashly attack

00:29.000 --> 00:31.520
But he did win the battle after all

00:31.520 --> 00:33.320
Your Majesty arrives

00:42.960 --> 00:45.160
Pay respects to Your Majesty

00:49.680 --> 00:50.600
Let's all speak

00:51.080 --> 00:51.960
What's the matter?

00:53.720 --> 00:54.360
Your Majesty

00:54.880 --> 00:55.440
I

00:55.920 --> 00:57.360
Wish to impeach Zhu Yuanzhi

00:58.920 --> 00:59.840
Not long ago

01:00.080 --> 01:01.120
Our Beishuo Army

01:01.480 --> 01:03.640
Engaged in close combat with Wuzhao's Shixin division

01:04.160 --> 01:05.720
The Ministry of War ordered General Zhu

01:06.160 --> 01:07.280
After repelling the enemy

01:07.600 --> 01:08.840
To withdraw and defend the base

01:09.600 --> 01:11.320
But General Zhu did not follow orders

01:11.320 --> 01:12.400
Privately advanced recklessly

01:12.440 --> 01:14.560
Actually pursued deep into Wuzhao territory

01:14.960 --> 01:17.480
Causing heavy losses to our troops

01:17.960 --> 01:20.000
And disrupted Your Majesty's approved battle plan

01:20.000 --> 01:21.360
Completely

01:22.200 --> 01:23.560
But no matter what

01:23.720 --> 01:25.520
General Zhu achieved a great victory this time

01:25.840 --> 01:27.040
The entire southern Pingzhou

01:27.040 --> 01:28.560
Was recovered by the Beishuo Army

01:28.680 --> 01:29.480
I think

01:29.600 --> 01:30.880
Not only should he not be punished

01:30.920 --> 01:32.160
But should be heavily rewarded

01:32.360 --> 01:34.720
To encourage the enterprising spirit of all

01:35.160 --> 01:36.080
I remember

01:36.280 --> 01:38.120
The court only gave General Zhu

01:38.120 --> 01:39.400
Supplies to repel the enemy

01:40.000 --> 01:42.000
The money for his campaign

01:42.200 --> 01:43.400
Where did it come from?

01:44.400 --> 01:45.400
This Zhu Yuanzhi

01:45.600 --> 01:47.320
Is almost declaring himself king

01:47.480 --> 01:48.360
He uses

01:50.480 --> 01:52.640
Your Majesty's land reform as a banner

01:53.200 --> 01:54.040
In Qingzhou

01:54.160 --> 01:55.520
Extensively seized land

01:55.600 --> 01:56.720
Directly distributed to the army

01:57.440 --> 01:58.520
But General Zhu

01:58.520 --> 02:00.920
Did successfully implement Your Majesty's new policies

02:01.120 --> 02:02.800
This is a great merit

02:04.520 --> 02:06.800
Forcibly seized from great families

02:07.120 --> 02:08.680
Privately divided court land

02:08.960 --> 02:09.480
This

02:09.600 --> 02:10.480
Is clearly

02:11.000 --> 02:12.120
Bandit behavior

02:14.040 --> 02:14.720
Alright, alright

02:14.720 --> 02:15.520
Stop arguing

02:16.200 --> 02:17.360
Let's put this matter aside for now

02:17.800 --> 02:18.680
Discuss another day

02:19.920 --> 02:20.680
Court dismissed

02:31.520 --> 02:32.520
This phoenix

02:33.000 --> 02:33.960
Has gotten fat recently

02:34.840 --> 02:35.520
It seems

02:36.080 --> 02:38.120
Fan Zhong's meals are quite good

02:41.120 --> 02:41.880
Let's talk

02:42.200 --> 02:43.320
About General Zhu's matter

02:44.720 --> 02:45.640
What do you think?

02:46.000 --> 02:47.520
Although General Zhu won a small victory

02:48.280 --> 02:50.160
He so flagrantly ignored court orders

02:50.360 --> 02:51.680
If something major happens in the future

02:51.880 --> 02:53.360
And General Zhu still acts willfully

02:53.640 --> 02:55.200
Cannot coordinate closely with the center

02:55.880 --> 02:57.400
This would be a catastrophic hole

02:59.440 --> 03:00.200
Your son believes

03:00.560 --> 03:01.920
We cannot have wishful thinking

03:02.440 --> 03:03.080
Should be punished

03:03.920 --> 03:04.640
A general in the field

03:04.920 --> 03:06.160
May not always follow the ruler's orders

03:07.040 --> 03:08.520
The battlefield changes in an instant

03:08.960 --> 03:10.680
If everything follows central orders

03:10.880 --> 03:12.000
Then how do we seize opportunities?

03:12.160 --> 03:12.920
Since ancient times

03:13.080 --> 03:14.680
Victory and defeat are decided in an instant

03:16.320 --> 03:16.800
Father

03:17.600 --> 03:18.360
Your son believes

03:18.840 --> 03:20.080
General Zhu's intentions are correct

03:20.400 --> 03:21.440
And he's brave and decisive

03:21.720 --> 03:22.400
Should be rewarded

03:22.640 --> 03:23.880
Xuan shall prosper
